lines.text: Well, in that event, Constable, I certainly can't do her any harm.

[fires her gun]
Murderer, you killed them. You killed them all.
Forgive me, Steven, I thought it was you. He always waited until you came home, so I thought it was you.
The only thing that keeps me from cracking you in the jaw is the almost certain possibility that it would break your neck.
